name: Grapes
description: Do you need sweetness in your life? Try the world's plumpiest grapes from the Uco Valley in Chile, worth every dollar! Buy now!

name: Watermelons
description: These delicious watermelons descend directly from those cultivated in ancient Rome. These are by no means watery, organic taste!

name: Apples
description: Our organic apples sure keep the doctors away, unlike these fumigated apples you can find in supermarket, ours are actually good for your health!

name: Strawberry
description: Our greenhouse-grown strawberries retain their taste the whole year. Why wait for winter when you can have 'em whenever you want?

name: Tomatoes
description: Fine mexican tomatoes, cultivated in the first cultivator's original swamps in Mochica, Mexico. Extra tasty, truly original flavor!

name: Red Peppers
description: Fine red peppers imported directly from Brazil, extra plumpy, ideal for pizza with ham. What are you waiting for?

name: Lettuce
description: Our butter lettuce is the freshest you will ever find. Only on our customer's order we uproot the plant! Can you resist it?

name: Carrots
description: Good old carrots, freshly uprooted on the customer's order. Do not eat these dry carrots from the market, try fresh, never go back!
